ZH: 我们在楼梯上安装了栏杆，以保证安全。
EN: We installed a railing on the staircase to ensure safety.

ZH: 她站在栏杆旁边，俯视着美丽的花园。
EN: She stood beside the railing, looking down at the beautiful garden.

ZH: 这座桥的栏杆非常结实，能够承受大量的重量。
EN: The railing of this bridge is very sturdy and can withstand a large amount of weight.

ZH: 我们在露台上放了一张桌子和几把椅子，旁边是一个铁制的栏杆。
EN: We placed a table and some chairs on the terrace, next to an iron railing.

ZH: 孩子们在栏杆上玩得很开心，不停地爬上爬下。
EN: The children had a great time playing on the railing, constantly climbing up and down.

ZH: 这个公园里的栏杆都刷成了亮黄色，以吸引游客的注意力。
EN: The railings in this park are painted bright yellow to catch the attention of visitors.

ZH: 我把我的自行车锁在栏杆上，因为没有任何地方可以停放。
EN: I locked my bicycle to the railing because there was no place to park.

ZH: 随着热气球升上天空，围绕篮子的铁栏杆成为了我们的保护。
EN: As the hot air balloon ascended into the sky, the iron railings around the basket became our protection.

ZH: 这个公园设有残疾人专用栏杆，以方便他们进入各个区域。
EN: This park has specially designed railings for disabled people, making it easier for them to access different areas.

ZH: 她拿着一个陌生人递给她的钱包，寻找附近的栏杆来放上面。
EN: She held a wallet given to her by a stranger, looking for a nearby railing to place it on.

ZH: 灯光照亮了树林中的栏杆，增加了夜晚的安全性。
EN: The lights illuminated the railings in the woods, increasing safety at night.

ZH: 这个游乐园里的过山车上都有栏杆，以确保乘客的安全。
EN: The roller coasters in this amusement park have railings, ensuring the safety of the passengers.

ZH: 数百人站在栏杆前，迎接演唱会开始的那一刻。
EN: Hundreds of people stood in front of the railing, waiting for the moment the concert would begin.

ZH: 高山上的栏杆给登山者提供了额外的支撑力，帮助他们攀登。
EN: The railings on the mountains provide climbers with extra support to help them ascend.

ZH: 他们围绕操场的四周安装了高大的栏杆，以保护孩子们的安全。
EN: They installed tall railings around the perimeter of the playground to protect the safety of the children.

