EN: The balcony of this house has metal railings, adding to the overall aesthetic appearance.

ZH: 沿河岸散步时，人们常常依靠栏杆，欣赏河流的美景。
EN: People often rely on the railings while strolling along the riverbank, admiring the beauty of the river.

ZH: 她紧紧抓住栏杆，不敢往下看，因为她害怕高度。
EN: She held onto the railing tightly, afraid to look down because she had a fear of heights.
